                Mr. Monslow  (Barrow-in-Furness)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ed647e29-33b8-484e-84ea-b918217c699e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-11-15/debates/3f3f7014-b819-41fd-8cea-fa274c2b5a81/IronAndSteelBill#contribution-ed647e29-33b8-484e-84ea-b918217c699e">
