                Mr. John R. Thomas  (Dover)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-75edf64e-a75b-4889-908f-f18d0c9c0599" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
